  # VirtIo Support
  VirtioLib|OvmfPkg/Library/VirtioLib/VirtioLib.inf
  VirtioMmioDeviceLib|OvmfPkg/Library/VirtioMmioDeviceLib/VirtioMmioDeviceLib.inf

